author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Deutsche Industrie REIT-AG Acquires Further Commercial Property In Neustadt-Glewe
text:
Feb 28 (Reuters) - DEUTSCHE INDUSTRIE REIT AG:
* DGAP-NEWS: DEUTSCHE INDUSTRIE REIT-AG: DEUTSCHE INDUSTRIE REIT-AG ACQUIRES FURTHER COMMERCIAL PROPERTIES IN DORTMUND, BOCHUM, WITTEN AND NEUSTADT-GLEWE
* ‍PROPERTY IN NEUSTADT-GLEWE WAS ACQUIRED FOR EUR 1.65 MLN​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
